590
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:26,600
Of course not.

591
00:33:29,280 --> 00:33:31,000
It's a question you asked,

592
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:32,560
but you forgot the answer.

593
00:33:33,560 --> 00:33:35,480
Use the instruments.

594
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:36,560
But...

595
00:33:36,560 --> 00:33:38,440
Why are you sure
abnormalities can be seen in a month?

596
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:42,560
What's the patient's walking problem?

597
00:33:47,560 --> 00:33:49,040
He swaggered,

598
00:33:49,040 --> 00:33:50,200
swayed,

599
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:51,560
and shuffled.

600
00:33:51,560 --> 00:33:53,840
What diseases do such symptoms indicate?

601
00:33:53,840 --> 00:33:54,720
A drunkard look,

602
00:33:55,560 --> 00:33:56,560
leg weakness,

603
00:33:57,280 --> 00:33:58,920
and cerebellar ataxia.

604
00:33:59,080 --> 00:34:00,560
What's his speaking problem?

605
00:34:02,560 --> 00:34:03,560
He lisped

606
00:34:03,560 --> 00:34:04,560
and stuttered.

607
00:34:05,680 --> 00:34:06,560
Dysarthria.

608
00:34:06,920 --> 00:34:08,080
What did he complain about?

609
00:34:08,560 --> 00:34:09,560
When you were downstairs,

610
00:34:09,560 --> 00:34:11,560
I could shoot your head off.

611
00:34:12,230 --> 00:34:13,670
But now, I can't.

612
00:34:13,670 --> 00:34:14,560
His skill decreased.

613
00:34:18,150 --> 00:34:20,440
Limb flexibility decreased.

614
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:22,040
So?

615
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:25,880
So, the lesion may be in...

616
00:34:29,710 --> 00:34:30,560
In his brainstem.

617
00:34:31,960 --> 00:34:32,760
Not too bad.

618
00:34:33,440 --> 00:34:34,960
You haven't totally forgotten it.

619
00:34:39,150 --> 00:34:41,560
The imaging technology
is so advanced now.

620
00:34:42,960 --> 00:34:45,120
How come we can't see a lesion?

621
00:34:45,230 --> 00:34:47,040
Maybe it's in an odd position.

622
00:34:47,280 --> 00:34:49,120
Or maybe it's the initial phase.

623
00:34:50,630 --> 00:34:51,670
But anyway,

624
00:34:52,150 --> 00:34:53,440
doctors like us

625
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:55,230
can't neglect every tiny little signal

626
00:34:55,560 --> 00:34:58,320
from a patient's body.

627
00:35:00,820 --> 00:35:01,700
