645
00:35:49,560 --> 00:35:50,200
You're wrong.

646
00:35:51,160 --> 00:35:52,560
We should trust Dr. Gu.

647
00:35:57,100 --> 00:35:59,660
[Friendship Hospital]

648
00:36:00,240 --> 00:36:01,240
General!

649
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:02,840
What are you doing?

650
00:36:02,880 --> 00:36:04,560
I'll go get in there.
I'll be wherever the General is.

651
00:36:04,680 --> 00:36:06,560
He said he stayed wherever General was.

652
00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:08,560
Let him in.

653
00:36:11,040 --> 00:36:12,520
The doctor said you could get in.

654
00:36:12,520 --> 00:36:13,480
But you have to obey

655
00:36:13,480 --> 00:36:14,200
the aseptic rule.

656
00:36:14,200 --> 00:36:14,800
Come with me.

657
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:18,360
Boss,

658
00:36:18,600 --> 00:36:19,680
wherever you go, I'll go.

659
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:21,360
I'll even die with you.

660
00:36:21,840 --> 00:36:24,000
No one will die unless your hands shake.

661
00:36:24,920 --> 00:36:25,400
You...

662
00:36:25,600 --> 00:36:26,920
Die with you?

663
00:36:27,560 --> 00:36:29,320
Then my life would be tragic.

664
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:54,800
It's been a long time.

665
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:56,560
Can he succeed?

666
00:36:59,320 --> 00:37:00,320
I told you.

667
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:03,120
He can't do a brainstem surgery.

668
00:37:03,640 --> 00:37:04,600
Dr. Gu

669
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:07,360
insisted on risking the General's life.

670
00:37:08,720 --> 00:37:11,000
Before irreversible damage is done,

671
00:37:11,120 --> 00:37:12,560
it's not too late to close his skull.

672
00:37:16,480 --> 00:37:17,800
The surgery isn't over.

673
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:19,120
Don't jump to conclusions.

674
00:37:23,200 --> 00:37:25,320
The blood pressure is dropping.

675
00:37:26,120 --> 00:37:27,240
The blood pressure is dropping.

676
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:30,560
Dr. Gu,

677
00:37:30,560 --> 00:37:32,080
put down your scalpel immediately.

678
00:37:32,080 --> 00:37:32,960
Or I'll hold you responsible

679
00:37:32,960 --> 00:37:34,000
on behalf of the Health Commission.

680
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,280
Leave everything to Dr. Eliot.

681
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:38,280
Get out of the way. Or I'll kill you.

682
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:45,720
Get out now!

683
00:37:58,720 --> 00:38:00,960
You're not approaching Dr. Gu

684
00:38:00,960 --> 00:38:02,160
unless I'm dead.

685
00:38:06,880 --> 00:38:09,360
No one can stop Dr. Gu in his surgery.

686
00:38:09,520 --> 00:38:11,920
Nobody shall disturb a surgeon.

687
00:38:12,040 --> 00:38:12,920
Miss Su,

688
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:14,080
you're a mere interpreter.

689
00:38:14,360 --> 00:38:16,160
You're unqualified
to comment on the surgery.

690
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:18,440
It's not too late to stop it now.

691
00:38:18,440 --> 00:38:20,080
I graduated in clinical medicine

692
00:38:20,080 --> 00:38:21,280
from Huaren Medical University.

693
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:22,560
I have a physician's certificate.

694
00:38:22,560 --> 00:38:24,720
I answer for whatever I say.

695
00:38:24,960 --> 00:38:26,280
If anything happens to General,

696
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:27,800
none of your guys can live.

697
00:38:39,560 --> 00:38:40,560
The lesion is in his medulla.

698
00:38:42,320 --> 00:38:43,640
The lesion is in his medulla.

699
00:38:44,720 --> 00:38:46,040
This is unbelievable.

700
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:58,640
Did you guys catch that?

701
00:38:59,280 --> 00:39:00,880
I think you should consider

702
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:03,120
how to apologize to Dr. Gu later.

703
00:39:12,400 --> 00:39:13,640
Put down the values.

704
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:16,900
Why isn't General waking up?

705
00:39:16,900 --> 00:39:18,060
The surgery has been over for so long.

706
00:39:18,420 --> 00:39:20,020
You mustn't go!

707
00:39:20,020 --> 00:39:21,620
You quack!

708
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:24,480
General wouldn't wake up so soon.

709
00:39:24,480 --> 00:39:25,960
But the surgery was very successful.

710
00:39:25,960 --> 00:39:28,240
Dr. Gu did a perfect job.

711
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:29,920
The lesion was perfectly removed, too.

712
00:39:29,920 --> 00:39:31,200
I underestimated him.

713
00:39:31,640 --> 00:39:33,160
You were wrong?

714
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,120
Dr. Eliot.

715
00:39:49,200 --> 00:39:50,200
Just now,

716
00:39:51,040 --> 00:39:51,840
