717
00:39:56,760 --> 00:39:58,360
As you said,

718
00:39:58,360 --> 00:39:59,720
Dr. Gu is an excellent doctor.

719
00:40:00,720 --> 00:40:02,800
I'll apologize to him

720
00:40:02,800 --> 00:40:04,040
