721
00:40:04,560 --> 00:40:05,680
Dr. Gu,

722
00:40:06,280 --> 00:40:07,080
I'm sorry.

723
00:40:07,600 --> 00:40:09,160
You were just worried about General.

724
00:40:09,840 --> 00:40:11,040
When we have the biopsy result,

725
00:40:11,040 --> 00:40:12,560
