726
00:40:13,040 --> 00:40:13,920
Thanks.

727
00:40:29,800 --> 00:40:30,800
What shall I do?

728
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:33,560
What now?

729
00:40:34,200 --> 00:40:35,720
In the operating room,

730
00:40:36,040 --> 00:40:37,880
