734
00:40:47,080 --> 00:40:49,120
I didn't. Don't overthink it.

735
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:51,840
You defended me in front of a gun.

736
00:40:52,480 --> 00:40:53,560
I have to overthink it.

737
00:40:54,640 --> 00:40:55,560
Just now,

738
00:40:56,560 --> 00:40:58,720
