745
00:41:14,560 --> 00:41:15,560
Don't pretend you understand.

746
00:41:16,040 --> 00:41:17,040
You didn't?

747
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:21,880
Maybe I heard what your heart said.

748
00:41:33,040 --> 00:41:34,040
Su Wei'an.

749
00:41:36,160 --> 00:41:37,160
Never

750
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:40,240
