751
00:41:40,960 --> 00:41:43,160
You can't risk your own life.

752
00:41:44,560 --> 00:41:46,120
Not even for me.

753
00:41:48,560 --> 00:41:50,160
When you're alive,

754
00:41:50,560 --> 00:41:52,200
