755
00:41:54,560 --> 00:41:56,560
It's worth it
to exchange my life for yours.

756
00:41:56,880 --> 00:41:57,720
I told you.

757
00:41:58,080 --> 00:41:59,560
Never say this again.

758
00:42:00,560 --> 00:42:02,400
Nobody's life

759
00:42:02,400 --> 00:42:04,240
