than someone else's.

760
00:42:13,920 --> 00:42:15,560
Wait a minute.

761
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:23,120
What? Know you were wrong?

762
00:42:24,560 --> 00:42:26,320
Didn't you just say

763
00:42:27,720 --> 00:42:29,440
